Package: quanteda.extras
Title: Additional Corpus Functions for quanteda
Version: 1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "David",
           family = "Brown",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "dwb2@andrew.cmu.edu",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7745-6354"))
Description:
	The package includes common corpus functions that expand
	the utility of quanteda. These include functions for 
	calculating effect sizes, dispersions, and collocations.
